Packages file at the root of the system or the repository contains info about package and its files.

It has the following hierarchy:
{ category_name = {
    package_name = {
        system_dir_name = { file1, file2, ... },
        ... 
        },
    ...
    },
...
}

Where system_dir_name is one of DIRS, defined in the beginning of startup and installer. Some of these are root, core, help, lib, bin, etc.
